  "description": "Create Echo dirty state loop animation as a horizontal sprite strip. Echo sprite frame size is 40x40px. Primary body color #FFA300, cheek patch #FF004D, crest #FFEC27, beak+feet #AB5236, eyes #1D2B53. Eyes are 2x2px blocks. No additional colors beyond the pico8_16 palette. No anti-aliasing; 1px steps only. Animation: 3 frames, 2 FPS, loop infinite. Spritesheet 120x40px. Expression: eyes half-closed (each eye is a 2x1 #1D2B53 line at the top row of the eye area). Crest down by +2px (lower than idle). Do not include dust particles inside the character spritesheet; dust particles are separate VFX assets.",
